{"image_id": "MKC_2015_page_70", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "68", "bbox": [125.0, 1584.3, 141.3, 1602.3]}, {"text": "16. BUSINESS SEGMENTS AND GEOGRAPHIC AREAS", "bbox": [125.0, 109.2, 543.6, 132.1]}, {"text": "Business Segments", "bbox": [125.0, 143.6, 279.0, 166.5]}, {"text": "We operate in two business segments: consumer and industrial. The", "bbox": [125.0, 166.8, 607.4, 189.4]}, {"text": "consumer and industrial segments manufacture, market and distrib-", "bbox": [125.0, 189.7, 596.7, 212.3]}, {"text": "ute spices, seasoning mixes, condiments and other flavorful products", "bbox": [125.0, 212.6, 604.9, 235.2]}, {"text": "throughout the world. Our consumer segment sells to retail channels,", "bbox": [125.0, 235.6, 610.3, 258.1]}, {"text": "including grocery, mass merchandise, warehouse clubs, discount and", "bbox": [125.0, 258.5, 607.8, 281.0]}, {"text": "drug stores, and e-commerce under the “McCormick” brand and a", "bbox": [125.0, 281.4, 588.4, 303.9]}, {"text": "variety of brands around the world, including “Lawry’s,” “Zatarain’s,”", "bbox": [125.0, 304.3, 609.5, 326.8]}, {"text": "“Simply Asia,” “Thai Kitchen,” “Ducros,” “Vahiné,” “Schwartz,” “Club", "bbox": [125.0, 327.2, 605.3, 349.8]}, {"text": "House,” “Kamis,” “Kohinoor,” “DaQiao,” “Drogheria & Alimentari”", "bbox": [125.0, 350.1, 586.3, 372.7]}, {"text": "and “Stubb’s.” Our industrial segment sells to food manufacturers", "bbox": [125.0, 373.0, 587.5, 395.6]}, {"text": "and the foodservice industry both directly and indirectly through", "bbox": [125.0, 395.9, 576.5, 418.5]}, {"text": "distributors.", "bbox": [125.0, 418.9, 208.8, 441.4]}, {"text": "In each of our segments, we produce and sell many individual", "bbox": [125.0, 464.7, 562.6, 487.2]}, {"text": "products which are similar in composition and nature. With their", "bbox": [125.0, 487.6, 582.1, 510.1]}, {"text": "primary attribute being flavor, we regard the products within each", "bbox": [125.0, 510.5, 595.1, 533.1]}, {"text": "of our segments to be fairly homogenous. It is impracticable to seg-", "bbox": [125.0, 533.4, 596.3, 556.0]}, {"text": "regate and identify sales and profits for each of these individual", "bbox": [125.0, 556.3, 576.5, 578.9]}, {"text": "product lines.", "bbox": [125.0, 579.2, 219.2, 601.8]}, {"text": "We measure segment performance based on operating income", "bbox": [125.0, 625.1, 567.8, 647.6]}, {"text": "excluding special charges and loss on voluntary pension settlement", "bbox": [125.0, 648.0, 598.1, 670.5]}, {"text": "as these activities are managed separately from the business seg-", "bbox": [668.8, 109.4, 1132.2, 131.9]}, {"text": "ments. Although the segments are managed separately due to their", "bbox": [668.8, 132.3, 1144.2, 154.9]}, {"text": "distinct distribution channels and marketing strategies, manufac­", "bbox": [668.8, 155.2, 1121.9, 177.8]}, {"text": "turing and warehousing are often integrated to maximize cost effi-", "bbox": [668.8, 178.1, 1133.5, 200.7]}, {"text": "ciencies. We do not segregate jointly utilized assets by individual", "bbox": [668.8, 201.0, 1127.1, 223.6]}, {"text": "segment for internal reporting, evaluating performance or allocating", "bbox": [668.8, 223.9, 1147.5, 246.5]}, {"text": "capital. Therefore, asset-related information has been disclosed in", "bbox": [668.8, 246.9, 1135.8, 269.4]}, {"text": "the aggregate.", "bbox": [668.8, 269.8, 770.7, 292.3]}, {"text": "We have a large number of customers for our products. Sales to", "bbox": [668.8, 315.6, 1123.5, 338.2]}, {"text": "one of our consumer segment customers, Wal-Mart Stores, Inc.,", "bbox": [668.8, 338.5, 1119.9, 361.1]}, {"text": "accounted for 11% of consolidated sales in 2015, 11% of consoli-", "bbox": [668.8, 361.4, 1121.2, 384.0]}, {"text": "dated sales in 2014 and 12% of consolidated sales in 2013. Sales to", "bbox": [668.8, 384.3, 1145.8, 406.9]}, {"text": "one of our industrial segment customers, PepsiCo, Inc., accounted", "bbox": [668.8, 407.2, 1131.5, 429.8]}, {"text": "for 11% of consolidated sales in 2015, 2014 and 2013.", "bbox": [668.8, 430.2, 1043.6, 452.7]}, {"text": "Accounting policies for measuring segment operating income and", "bbox": [668.8, 476.0, 1128.4, 498.5]}, {"text": "assets are consistent with those described in note 1. Because of", "bbox": [668.8, 498.9, 1122.8, 521.5]}, {"text": "integrated manufacturing for certain products within the segments,", "bbox": [668.8, 521.8, 1143.5, 544.4]}, {"text": "products are not sold from one segment to another but rather inven-", "bbox": [668.8, 544.7, 1144.3, 567.3]}, {"text": "tory is transferred at cost. Inter-segment sales are not material.", "bbox": [668.8, 567.6, 1117.3, 590.2]}, {"text": "Corporate assets include cash, deferred taxes, investments and", "bbox": [668.8, 590.5, 1121.0, 613.1]}, {"text": "certain fixed assets.", "bbox": [668.8, 613.5, 814.5, 636.0]}, {"text": "Business Segment Results", "bbox": [125.0, 693.4, 333.0, 716.3]}, {"text": "(millions)", "bbox": [131.2, 746.9, 182.4, 765.7]}, {"text": "Consumer", "bbox": [718.7, 746.9, 775.1, 765.7]}, {"text": "Industrial", "bbox": [814.2, 746.9, 867.1, 765.7]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [919.1, 728.1, 950.0, 746.9]}, {"text": "segments", "bbox": [905.5, 746.9, 960.2, 765.7]}, {"text": "Corporate", "bbox": [998.3, 728.1, 1057.3, 746.9]}, {"text": "& other", "bbox": [1004.6, 746.9, 1047.5, 765.7]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [1104.0, 746.9, 1131.4, 765.7]}, {"text": "2015", "bbox": [131.2, 775.0, 162.3, 795.6]}, {"text": "Net sales", "bbox": [131.2, 795.8, 196.6, 816.5]}, {"text": "$2,635.2", "bbox": [721.1, 795.8, 772.9, 816.5]}, {"text": "$1,661.1", "bbox": [814.9, 795.8, 866.7, 816.5]}, {"text": "$4,296.3", "bbox": [906.5, 795.8, 958.3, 816.5]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [1029.2, 795.8, 1045.8, 816.5]}, {"text": "$\b4,296.3", "bbox": [1091.7, 795.8, 1143.8, 816.5]}, {"text": "Operating income excluding special charges", "bbox": [131.2, 816.7, 438.7, 837.3]}, {"text": "456.1", "bbox": [739.6, 816.7